==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Acetabulifera
<hw>Ac`e*tab`u*lif"e*ra</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL. See <er>Acetabuliferous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The division of Cephalopoda in which the arms are furnished with
cup-shaped suckers, as the cuttlefishes, squids, and octopus; the
Dibranchiata. See <er>Cephalopoda</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Acetabuliferous</ent>⟦br⟧
